freenet.client.async
Class SplitFileFetcher

java.lang.Object
  freenet.client.async.SplitFileFetcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientGetState, HasKeyListener
public class SplitFileFetcher
extends Object
implements ClientGetState, HasKeyListener

Fetch a splitfile, decompress it if need be, and return it to the GetCompletionCallback. Most of the work is done by the segments, and we do not need a thread.
